title: Ring Clock Watch Face
summary: Ring Clock is simple clock with digital time and analog rings.
description: Ring Clock is simple clock with digital time and analog rings. The rings are related to time: inner yellow ring gets brighter, when hour gets bigger. Both cyan and magenta rings represents minutes and seconds. The rings provide brights symbol of time for late night fun. The clock is black at midnight to indicate that party just started for next day.
